data.description: *** Multiple offers received*** Best and final by 1pm February 14th. Charming two bed, one bath home in the heart of the Webber-Camden neighborhood. This lovely home has an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, wood floors, an updated full bath and large two car garage. Relax and unwind on the welcoming front porch, adding a touch of character to this adorable home. You will enjoy the large yard with a wood fence in the middle of this delightful established community.
